name: Timed Killer
description:
A Game About A Secret Killer That Has To Spend As Little Time As Possible On A Job To Make The Most Money Out Of It!

Game Made In Roughly 3 Days
Everything  has been made from scratch.
The Less Time You Spend On A Given Level, The More Money You Get.

The Game Comes with 2 Modes
Normal : 10 Levels and 1 Boss
Endless : Infinite Enemies, 1 Shot 1 Kill, HP Regeneration

I Am Really Bad With Art So I'm Sorry About The Low Quality Art.

Any Feedback Would Be Greatly Appreciated!
